国关系不应再为历史恩怨对抗。 路透社、共同社报道截图 尹锡悦：日本已深刻道歉，日韩不应再为历史恩怨对抗"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c42732e8be0202fda486ddeabb75e14c_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "165 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589897589"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iw/aiiNvzyq03EAMaCDkzMzY5ODk2IN7wyaAGMAI4f0AGcgk1ODk4OTc1ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1678947064.3452046", "card_id": "Q_589901230", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价国漫《画江湖之不良人 》第六季第 4 集？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0a7df372bf22c64a7bdcc055339290ee_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "140 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589901230"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "导演亲自答", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iw/aiiNvzyq03EAMaCDkzMzcwNzE0IO/9yaAGMAA4KkAHcgk1ODk5MDEyMzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1678947064.3462377", "card_id": "Q_589756629", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 249}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待刘作虎晒出 Find X6 系列样张对比友商？你是否看好 OPPO 这次在影像旗舰上的发力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如何看待刘作虎在微博上所放出的 OPPO Find X6 系